Package com.microsoft.azure.management.trafficmanager

This package contains the resource management traffic manager class, interface, and associated configuration and utility classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    EndpointOperations
    Operations for managing Traffic Manager endpoints.
    ProfileOperations
    Operations for managing Traffic Manager profiles.
    TrafficManagerManagementClient
    Client for creating, updating, listing and deleting Azure Traffic Manager profiles (see http://azure.microsoft.com/en-gb/documentation/articles/traffic-manager-overview/ for more information)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EndpointOperationsImpl
    Operations for managing Traffic Manager endpoints.
    Exports
    The Class Exports.
    ProfileOperationsImpl
    Operations for managing Traffic Manager profiles.
    TrafficManagerManagementClientImpl
    Client for creating, updating, listing and deleting Azure Traffic Manager profiles (see http://azure.microsoft.com/en-gb/documentation/articles/traffic-manager-overview/ for more information)
    TrafficManagerManagementService
    Access service management functionality.
